{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n  <body>\n    <h2>最新天文台天氣報告｜未來五天香港天氣預報</h2>\n    <p>天文台展望，未來一兩日大致多雲，但明早氣溫仍然較低。星期日日間炎熱，稍後天氣漸轉不穩定。</p>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>4月30日(四)</cell>\n        <cell>5月1日(五)</cell>\n        <cell>5月2日(六)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n        <cell>26度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>20度</cell>\n        <cell>22度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風4至5級，初時離岸間中6級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東北風4級，離岸5級。</cell>\n        <cell>東至東南風3至4級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>50-80%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。早上天氣較涼，日間部分時間有陽光及乾燥。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲。稍後有一兩陣驟雨。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，初時有一兩陣驟雨。下午部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n    <table>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>日期</cell>\n        <cell>5月3日(日)</cell>\n        <cell>5月4日(一)</cell>\n        <cell>5月5日(二)</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最高溫度</cell>\n        <cell>29度</cell>\n        <cell>28度</cell>\n        <cell>27度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>最低溫度</cell>\n        <cell>24度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n        <cell>23度</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>風向及級數</cell>\n        <cell>南風2至3級，晚上北風3級。</cell>\n        <cell>北至東北風3至4級。</cell>\n        <cell>東風4至5級。</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>濕度</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-95%</cell>\n        <cell>70-90%</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>顯著降雨概率</cell>\n        <cell>中高</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n        <cell>低</cell>\n      </row>\n      <row span=\"4\">\n        <cell>天氣</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，有幾陣驟雨。初時短暫時間有陽光。稍後驟雨較多，局部地區有雷暴。</cell>\n        <cell>大致多雲，初時有一兩陣驟雨。日間部分時間天色明朗。</cell>\n        <cell>短暫時間有陽光。</cell>\n      </row>\n    </table>\n  </body>\n</html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T23:13:57.162699+00:00","quality":{"score":1,"chars":499,"images":0,"source":"GoTrip","fallback":"none"}}